title: Remove Endorsement interface from frontend types
description:
Edit `src/frontend/src/lib/graphql/types.ts` to remove:
1. The `Endorsement` interface definition
2. The `endorsements` field from the `Builder` interface
Ensure TypeScript compiles successfully without these types.
acceptance_criteria:
- No `Endorsement` interface in types.ts
- No `endorsements` field on `Builder` interface
- `npx tsc --noEmit` passes with no errors
- Frontend builds successfully
